{
  "stem": "19921.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 385.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was just lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I got two shrapnels, that's true-- did not entered my uniform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When we were-- when we had that long stay in-- near the city of Warsaw there in Prag, I made myself a uniform.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] From-- I-- from-- I couldn't wear a coat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was just too bulky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I took the fabric from the coat and made a uniform out of it-- you know, jacket.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I made one for my captain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And because I didn't wear any coats, I had to pad it out should we stay warm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that padding saved my skin anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if that would have killed me or not-- but saved my skin-- just two shrapnels embedded in that cotton, didn't go through.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- but that was the, the one day two of my guys got hit, minor injuries, from shrapnels.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then the next day, they surrendered?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day, on, on the 2nd of May-- on the 2nd of May at 2:00 AM, they surrendered.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Crying a lot-- crying a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hug each other, and that was the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no shooting anymore going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That center were completely cleared from Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eventually, all Germans surrendered anyway on the 8th.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But Berlin as such surrendered officially on that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And no shooting was going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The only thing what we observed after that-- there were columns, thousands and thousands of German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't tell them where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was just signs posted-- this and this division or this and this regiment, go to here and there on this strasse.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were just following.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And thousands of them were passing by.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
